Text: Computer Technology SectionDear Member of the Computer Technology Section Our records indicate that you are a member of the Computer Technology Section of the State Bar of Texas yet are not currently subscribed to our Tech Tips email list so we wanted to send you a notice in the event you wish to subscribe to this free service from the Computer Technoilogy Section of the State Bar of Texas Subscribe by going to the mailroom on our website at mail Thank you Postmaster Computer Technology Section mailto
